<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
    Block the recurring "Vagabonds Hope for Alms" (charity beggars) quest.

    That is the Ideology Beggars QuestScriptDef (its name rule renders as "Vagabonds Hope for Alms"):
    a group of poor travelers periodically shows up begging for items. It's isRootSpecial (its
    GiveQuest_Beggars incident has baseChance 0), so it never comes from the random-quest roll - it's
    fired by a StorytellerCompProperties_OnOffCycle comp on the shared abstract BaseStoryteller (every
    ~60 days). Removing that comp (patches run before def inheritance resolves, so it propagates to
    every storyteller, The Antagonist included) stops the quest recurring. Other base comps untouched.

    Global by nature (no storyteller offers it), not scoped to The Antagonist. Gated on Ideology via
    MayRequire - without that DLC the beggars comp doesn't exist, so this is a no-op.
-->
<Patch>
    <Operation Class="PatchOperationRemove" MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Ideology">
        <xpath>Defs/StorytellerDef[@Name="BaseStoryteller"]/comps/li[incident="GiveQuest_Beggars"]</xpath>
    </Operation>
</Patch>
